HEADWORD: Proportionally
<hw>Pro*por"tion*al*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In
proportion; in due degree; adapted relatively; <as>as, all parts of the
building are <ex>proportionally</ex> large</as>.</def> <rj><au>Sir I.
Newton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

